## 3. Typography Rules

### Font Family
- **Heading**: Salesforce-Sans, fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif
- **Body**: Salesforce-Avant-Garde, fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif
- **Monospace**: ui-monospace, fallback: ui-monospace, monospace

### Hierarchy

| Role | Font | Size | Weight | Line Height | Letter Spacing |
|------|------|------|--------|-------------|----------------|
| H1 | Salesforce-Avant-Garde | 64px | 700 | 72px | -0.768px |
| H2 | Salesforce-Avant-Garde | 58px | 600 | 72.5px | -0.464px |
| H3 | Salesforce-Avant-Garde | 24px | 700 | 31.2px | normal |
| Body | Salesforce-Sans | 16px | 700 | 24px | -0.064px |
| Small | Salesforce-Sans | 15px | 700 | 1.4 | normal |
| Small | Salesforce-Sans | 14px | 700 | 1.4 | normal |

### Principles
- Heading weight: **700**
- Body weight: **400**
- Base size: 16px
- Line height: tight (1.15), normal (1.5), relaxed (1.75)

## 4. Component Stylings

### Buttons

**Primary**
- Background: `#2e0039`
- Text: `#ffffff`
- Padding: 0px
- Radius: 8px
- Font: 16px Salesforce-Avant-Garde weight 400

### Cards & Containers
- Background: `#696969`
- Border: 1px solid `#f2defe`
- Radius: 12px
- Shadow: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 10px 0px`

### Inputs & Forms
- Background: `#000000`
- Border: 1px solid `#f2defe`
- Radius: 8px
- Focus: 1px solid `#2e0039`
- Text: `#ffffff`
- Placeholder: `#f4ede4`


## 5. Layout Principles

### Spacing System
- Scale: 4px, 6px, 8px, 10px, 12px, 16px, 18px, 20px, 24px, 30px, 32px, 36px
- XS: 4px, SM: 8px, MD: 16px, LG: 24px, XL: 32px

### Border Radius Scale
- Small: 4px
- Medium: 8px
- Large: 12px
- Full: 9999px

### Grid
- Max content width: ~1200px
- Standard section padding: 32px – 36px

## 6. Depth & Elevation

| Level | Treatment | Use |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| Subtle | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 0px 32px 0px...` | Hover hints, small cards |
| Standard | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 10px 0px...` | Cards, dropdowns |
| Elevated | `rgb(97, 31, 105) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset...` | Modals, popovers |
| Deep | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 5px 20px 0px...` | Floating panels, toasts |

## 7. Do's and Don'ts

### Do
- Use `#2e0039` as the primary interactive/CTA color
- Use `#ffffff` for headings, `#f9edff` for body
- Keep border-radius consistent: 4px – 12px
- Use Salesforce-Sans for headings at weight 700
- Apply shadows from the elevation scale for depth
- Use `#f2defe` for all standard borders

### Don't
- Don't use pure white (#ffffff) for text — use `#ffffff`
- Don't mix border-radius sizes inconsistently
- Don't use colors outside the defined palette
- Don't use font weights not present in the type scale
- Don't skip the spacing scale — use the defined values

## 8. Responsive Behavior

### Breakpoints
| Name | Width | Key Changes |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Mobile | <640px | Single column, reduced heading sizes |
| Tablet | 640-1024px | 2-column grids, moderate padding |
| Desktop | 1024-1280px | Full layout |
| Large Desktop | >1280px | Centered content with generous margins |

### Collapsing Strategy
- Navigation: horizontal links → hamburger menu
- Feature cards: multi-column → single column stacked
- Typography scale compresses ~20% on mobile
- Spacing reduces proportionally

