- "Design a card: `#696969` background, 1px solid `#f2defe`, 12px radius. Shadow: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 10px 0px`. Title at 1.25rem weight 700, `#ffffff`. Body at 16px weight 400, `#f9edff`."

### Iteration Guide
1. Always use the defined color palette — no ad-hoc colors
2. Heading weight is 700, body weight is 400
3. Border radius: 4px (small), 8px (default), 12px (large)
4. Use the spacing scale: xs(4px), sm(8px), md(16px), lg(24px), xl(32px)
5. Shadow levels: sm, md, lg — use consistently
